# ── Sensitive data — NEVER commit ────────────────────────────────────────────
# This is a PII tool. Real spreadsheets, PDFs, the name→pseudonym crosswalk (the
# re-identification KEY), and the master list (real staff names + IDs) are all
# Confidential under IPA's data-classification policy and must never enter version
# control. The app reads the master list from a local file that each machine
# supplies out-of-band; MasterListRepository tolerates its absence.
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.xlsm
*.pdf
*_crosswalk.csv
# Master list and any other data CSVs (real names) — keep local, never commit.
finance_redactor/infrastructure/names/data/*.csv
